* Iron Raptor's stomach almost seemed to be in her ankles as Prowl had swooped down and caught hold of her, she looked down but that slight fear of hights never did seem to go away.
She then looked up at Prowl and saw that it was a strain on him to be carrying her, it was never easy to carry a 189 pound velociraptor. 
Iron Raptor just hoped that they wouldn't be attacked with her in such a volnerable state, not to mention that transformation would be virtually impossable.
She looked down again and tucked her feet under her, wrapping her tail around them. Her arms felt as if they were just about ready to fall off but she was sure that Prowl really didn't feel any better. She just hoped that they would get to base soon.*
